text: Dario Caviezel (born 12 July 1995) is a Swiss snowboarder. He competed in the 2017 FIS Snowboard World Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in parallel giant slalom. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of Switzerland Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics
